ish (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/selectstart_event\"><code>selectstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchcancel_event\"><code>touchcancel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchend_event\"><code>touchend</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchmove_event\"><code>touchmove</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchstart_event\"><code>touchstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/visibilitychange_event\"><code>visibilitychange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"podsumowanie","title":"Podsumowanie","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Tworzy element podanego typu. Zauważ, że zwracana instancja implementuje interfejs Element, zatem można manipulować atrybutami bezpośrednio na zwróconym obiekcie.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sk.c5.82adnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">''element'' = document.createElement(''typ'')\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parametry","title":"Parametry","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><em>element</em>jest obiektem</li>\n <li><em>typ</em>jest ciągiem znaków oznaczającym typ tworzonego elementu</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ad","title":"Przykład","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;html&gt;\n&lt;head&gt;\n&lt;title&gt;||Praca z elementami||&lt;/title&gt;\n&lt;/head&gt;\n\n&lt;script type=\"text/javascript\"&gt;\nvar my_div = null;\nvar newDiv = null;\n\nfunction addElement()\n{\n  // tworzy nowy element div\n  // i daje jego zawartość\n  newDiv = document.createElement(\"div\");\n  newDiv.innerHTML = \"&lt;h1&gt;Hi there and greetings!&lt;/h1&gt;\";\n\n  // add the newly created element and it's content into the DOM\n  my_div = document.getElementById(\"org_div1\");\n  document.body.insertBefore(newDiv, my_div);\n}\n\n&lt;/script&gt;\n\n&lt;body onload=\"addElement()\"&gt;\n    &lt;div id='org_div1'&gt; The text above has been created dynamically.&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/body&gt;\n&lt;/html&gt;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"uwagi","title":"Uwagi","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Jeżeli znane są atrybuty o domyślnych wartościach, zostaną automatycznie utworzone i przypisane do elementu węzły tychże atrybutów.</p>\n\n<p>Aby utworzyć element o uściślonej nazwie i URI przestrzeni nazw, użyj metody <strong>createElementNS</strong>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacja","title":"Specyfikacja","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2000/REC-DOM-Level-2-Core-20001113/core.html#ID-2141741547\" rel=\" noopener\">createElement</a></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"noinclude\" id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Tworzy element podanego typu. Zauważ, że zwracana instancja implementuje interfejs Element, zatem można manipulować atrybutami bezpośrednio na zwróconym obiekcie.","popularity":0.0008,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Document.createElement()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Document.createElement()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Document.createElement()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"document.createElement","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Document.createElement()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Document.createElement()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Document.createElement()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"document.createElement","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Document.createElement()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Document.createElement()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/api/document/createelement","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/api/document/createelement/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API","title":"Lista Web API"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/Document","title":"document"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/Document/createElement","title":"document.createElement"}],"pageTitle":"document.createElement - Lista Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}